{"info": {"author": "miphreal", "author_email": "miphreal@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8"], "description": "<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/rofi-menu/\">\n        <img src=\"https://badge.fury.io/py/rofi-menu.svg\" alt=\"Package version\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n# rofi-menu\n\nRofi allows defining custom modes ([see the spec](https://github.com/davatorium/rofi/wiki/mode-Specs)).\n\nThis lib is a reference implementation with some extra \"sugar\".\n\nSimple demo:\n\n![custom menu](docs/demo.gif)\n\n## Installation\n\nUsing pip\n\n```sh\n$ pip install rofi-menu\n```\n\n## Example\n\nCreate a python script which will be used for rofi mode\ne.g. `example.py` (don't forget to mark it as executable -- `chmod +x ./example.py`)\n\nAssuming you installed `rofi-menu` into a virtual environment (let's say it's `~/.pyenv/versions/rofi/bin/python`).\nMake sure shebang points to the right python executable, e.g. `#!/home/user/pyenv/versions/rofi/bin/python`.\n```python\n#!/home/user/pyenv/versions/rofi/bin/python\nimport rofi_menu\n\n\nclass ProjectsMenu(rofi_menu.Menu):\n    prompt = \"Projects\"\n    items = [\n        rofi_menu.BackItem(),\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\"Project 1\", \"code-insiders ~/Develop/project1\"),\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\"Project 2\", \"code-insiders ~/Develop/project2\"),\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\"Project X\", \"code-insiders ~/Develop/projectx\"),\n    ]\n\n\nclass LogoutMenu(rofi_menu.Menu):\n    prompt = \"Logout\"\n    items = [\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\"Yes\", \"i3-msg exit\", flags={rofi_menu.FLAG_STYLE_URGENT}),\n        rofi_menu.ExitItem(\"No\", flags={rofi_menu.FLAG_STYLE_ACTIVE}),\n    ]\n\n\nclass MainMenu(rofi_menu.Menu):\n    prompt = \"menu\"\n    items = [\n        rofi_menu.TouchpadItem(),\n        rofi_menu.NestedMenu(\"Projects >\", ProjectsMenu()),\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\n            \"Downloads (show size)\", \"du -csh ~/Downloads\", show_output=True\n        ),\n        rofi_menu.NestedMenu(\"Second monitor\", rofi_menu.SecondMonitorMenu()),\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\"Lock screen\", \"i3lock -i ~/.config/i3/bg.png\"),\n        rofi_menu.ShellItem(\"Sleep\", \"systemctl suspend\"),\n        rofi_menu.NestedMenu(\"Logout\", LogoutMenu()),\n    ]\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    rofi_menu.run(MainMenu())\n```\n\nRun it as:\n\n```sh\n$ rofi -modi mymenu:/path/to/example.py -show mymenu\n```\n\nIt'll result in\n\n![rofi menu](docs/menu-example.png)", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/miphreal/python-rofi-menu", "keywords": "menu,rofi,rofi-mode", "license": "MIT", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "rofi-menu", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/rofi-menu/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/rofi-menu/", "project_urls": {"Documentation": "https://github.com/miphreal/python-rofi-menu", "Homepage": "https://github.com/miphreal/python-rofi-menu", "Repository": "https://github.com/miphreal/python-rofi-menu"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/rofi-menu/0.2.1/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": ">=3.6,<4.0", "summary": "Create rofi menus via python", "version": "0.2.1", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/rofi-menu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <img alt=\"Package version\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/d6af0ccba58e926f071969fe9a8b6972b4532c25/68747470733a2f2f62616467652e667572792e696f2f70792f726f66692d6d656e752e737667\">\n    </a>\n</p>\n<h1>rofi-menu</h1>\n<p>Rofi allows defining custom modes (<a href=\"https://github.com/davatorium/rofi/wiki/mode-Specs\" rel=\"nofollow\">see the spec</a>).</p>\n<p>This lib is a reference implementation with some extra \"sugar\".</p>\n<p>Simple demo:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"custom menu\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/6fc39c04029b162b0d2e54c934bdc300ba5be68f/646f63732f64656d6f2e676966\"></p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Using pip</p>\n<pre>$ pip install rofi-menu\n</pre>\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<p>Create a python script which will be used for rofi mode\ne.g. <code>example.py</code> (don't forget to mark it as executable -- <code>chmod +x ./example.py</code>)</p>\n<p>Assuming you installed <code>rofi-menu</code> into a virtual environment (let's say it's <code>~/.pyenv/versions/rofi/bin/python</code>).\nMake sure shebang points to the right python executable, e.g. <code>#!/home/user/pyenv/versions/rofi/bin/python</code>.</p>\n<pre><span class=\"ch\">#!/home/user/pyenv/versions/rofi/bin/python</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">rofi_menu</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">ProjectsMenu</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Menu</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">prompt</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Projects\"</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">items</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">BackItem</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Project 1\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"code-insiders ~/Develop/project1\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Project 2\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"code-insiders ~/Develop/project2\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Project X\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"code-insiders ~/Develop/projectx\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">LogoutMenu</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Menu</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">prompt</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Logout\"</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">items</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Yes\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"i3-msg exit\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">flags</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">FLAG_STYLE_URGENT</span><span class=\"p\">}),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ExitItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"No\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">flags</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">FLAG_STYLE_ACTIVE</span><span class=\"p\">}),</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">MainMenu</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Menu</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">prompt</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"menu\"</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">items</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">TouchpadItem</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NestedMenu</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Projects &gt;\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ProjectsMenu</span><span class=\"p\">()),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n            <span class=\"s2\">\"Downloads (show size)\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"du -csh ~/Downloads\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">show_output</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NestedMenu</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Second monitor\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecondMonitorMenu</span><span class=\"p\">()),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Lock screen\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"i3lock -i ~/.config/i3/bg.png\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ShellItem</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Sleep\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"systemctl suspend\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">NestedMenu</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Logout\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">LogoutMenu</span><span class=\"p\">()),</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"vm\">__name__</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"__main__\"</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">rofi_menu</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">run</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">MainMenu</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n</pre>\n<p>Run it as:</p>\n<pre>$ rofi -modi mymenu:/path/to/example.py -show mymenu\n</pre>\n<p>It'll result in</p>\n<p><img alt=\"rofi menu\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/adc921796b40a0ef37cf1c6b86c316282c7638ed/646f63732f6d656e752d6578616d706c652e706e67\"></p>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6908776, "releases": {"0.1.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "390db74e450bbed17f86a11bdf0c392e", "sha256": "b0aad3fabcda7859947bde2891d9bf916e89ee867d4b7ccdb14905fabb32641e"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "rofi_menu-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "390db74e450bbed17f86a11bdf0c392e", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": ">=3.8,<4.0", "size": 6120, "upload_time": "2020-03-29T19:40:53", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-03-29T19:40:53.789941Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/05/b2/1f080c2229d0d8c3d8bf74b8128c2ece047fa6049a20c4f68217fa30e0d0/rofi_menu-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "65f4c74a0defbd03a5b8c81b34aee683", "sha256": "d99507a253db06423bce653c9051bdd7a68cbf9f5231aad963f1ad6c515a7353"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "rofi-menu-0.1.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "65f4c74a0defbd03a5b8c81b34aee683", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.8,<4.0", "size": 4142, "upload_time": "2020-03-29T19:40:51", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-03-29T19:40:51